    <section id="tribute-info">
      <h3 id="headline">Here's some fun facts about our favorite snarky cat ! </h3>
      <ul>
        <li> On <strong>June 19th 1978</strong>, Garfield made his first appearance in newspapers. </li><br>
        <li> <strong> Lasagnas </strong> are Garfield's favorite dishes. </li><br>
        <li> Garfield hates <strong> Mondays </strong> and <strong> dogs</strong>. </li><br>
        <li> Jon Arbuckle is Garfield's <s> servant</s><strong> owner</strong>.</li><br>
         <li><strong>Pooky</strong> is Garfield's beloved teddy bear.</li><br>

         <li>Garfield also lives with  <strong>Odie</strong>, a rather simple-minded dog.</li> <br>

<li> <strong>Nermal</strong>, a kitten, is Garfield's rival.</li><br>

<li><strong>Arlene</strong> is Garfield's love interest, although she is not that much interested in him.</li><br>

        </ul>
